This got rave reviews from even the pickiest eaters. I didn't have coriander so I substituted cayenne pepper and cumin and it was still wonderful! Also made my own garden fresh salsa to go on top. Make this with the Tequila Shrimp recipe and spoon shrimp mixture on top. I also had corn tortillas on the side for sopping up the sauce.

