These were scrumptious! I took a very large red bell pepper, threw it in the processor with half a red onion. Sauteed it in the butter, then tossed it in with everything else. Used a ton of cilantro and the kids came over and tried to eat it before I cooked it! Unfried this would be great as a dip. Threw on a bit of green chile salsa and loved it.

